END OF PROJECT


INSTRUCTIONS (short):
1) Copy files into a folder, push to a GitHub repo.
2) Replace placeholder emails/numbers and update EmailJS keys in `js/main.js`.
3) Optionally sign up for EmailJS and create a template that uses `to_email` to route.
4) Enable GitHub Pages to publish.

If you'd like, I can now generate a zip file of these files ready for download. (If you want a serverless/email provider configuration, tell me which provider: EmailJS, Netlify Forms, Formspree or a custom server — I'll include exact setup steps & template.)
